to remove the boy...

1314
01:06:45,907 --> 01:06:48,325
 both boys,
from this home.

1315
01:06:48,493 --> 01:06:51,370
No, don't,
Ms. Grunion, please!

1316
01:06:51,537 --> 01:06:54,664
This is all my fault.
I started it.

1317
01:06:55,792 --> 01:06:57,376
I'm so sorry, Sherman.

1318
01:06:58,503 --> 01:07:01,254
You have nothing
to apologize for, Penny.

1319
01:07:01,422 --> 01:07:03,090
A dog should never
have been allowed

1320
01:07:03,216 --> 01:07:04,883
