in the first place.

1321
01:07:05,051 --> 01:07:06,176
Now, come along.

1322
01:07:06,344 --> 01:07:07,803
Ms. Grunion,
be careful!

1323
01:07:08,262 --> 01:07:10,097
Ah! Oh!

1324
01:07:10,181 --> 01:07:11,014
What's happening?

1325
01:07:16,104 --> 01:07:18,188
 Mr. Peabody, help!

1326
01:07:18,356 --> 01:07:19,523
Sherman!
Sherman!

1327
01:07:23,653 --> 01:07:25,153
 Oh!

1328
01:07:33,246 --> 01:07:35,163
