 Our cosmic doubles
combined in order to
reconcile a paradox...

1330
01:07:40,128 --> 01:07:42,712
in the space-time continuum.

1331
01:07:43,131 --> 01:07:44,631
Okay, that makes sense.

1332
01:07:45,091 --> 01:07:47,050
I don't know what
just happened here...

1333
01:07:47,218 --> 01:07:49,928
but I know it was wrong!

1334
01:07:50,096 --> 01:07:51,805
This boy is coming with me!
Mr. Peabody!

1335
01:07:52,223 --> 01:07:53,432
No, Ms. Grunion!
Ow! Let me go!

1336
01:07:53,641 --> 01:07:54,349
Get back here!

1337
01:07:55,059 --> 01:07:57,060
Ow! Ow! You're hurting me!

1338
01:08:00,064 --> 01:08:01,481
Oh! Oh!

1339
01:08:05,111 --> 01:08:07,195
He bit me!

1340
01:08:08,573 --> 01:08:10,449
He bit me!

1341
01:08:12,034 --> 01:08:13,577
Yes, hello, police.

1342
01:08:13,744 --> 01:08:15,662
I'd like to
report an assault.

1343
01:08:15,830 --> 01:08:16,830
A bite.

1344
01:08:16,998 --> 01:08:19,082
Mr. Peabody,
what are we gonna do?

1345
01:08:19,250 --> 01:08:20,667
 Get here
as soon as possible.

1346
01:08:20,835 --> 01:08:21,626
Run!

1347
01:08:22,795 --> 01:08:24,421
He's kidnapping
the children! Oh!

1348
01:08:27,592 --> 01:08:29,217
 I can't believe
you bit her, Mr. Peabody!

1349
01:08:29,385 --> 01:08:31,136
I know, Sherman,
it was wrong.

1350
01:08:31,304 --> 01:08:32,012
