to our proper timeline
and erase this mess.

1353
01:08:41,355 --> 01:08:44,858
There he is!
He's got my daughter
in that giant space apple!

1354
01:08:52,074 --> 01:08:53,909
 My face is numb.

1355
01:08:56,078 --> 01:08:57,537
Whoo-hoo!
Yes!

1356
01:08:58,831 --> 01:08:59,998
What's wrong?

1357
01:09:04,545 --> 01:09:05,921
time travel failed.

1358
01:09:06,380 --> 01:09:07,172
Oh, dear.

1359
01:09:07,590 --> 01:09:09,716
 What is it,
Mr. Peabody?

1360
01:09:09,884 --> 01:09:10,842
Our cosmic
doubles colliding...

1361
01:09:11,010 --> 01:09:12,636
ripped a hole
in the space-time continuum.

1362
01:09:13,054 --> 01:09:15,096
That's why we didn't
get to the past.

1363
01:09:18,309 --> 01:09:20,310
Hey, Peabody!

1364
01:09:20,478 --> 01:09:22,437
Looks like the past
is coming to us.

1365
01:09:24,357 --> 01:09:26,525
Oof! I will get you, dog!

1366
01:09:26,984 --> 01:09:28,610
And your little boy, too!

1367
01:09:31,572 --> 01:09:32,280
Penny!

1368
01:09:32,448 --> 01:09:33,448
My bride!

1369
01:09:37,286 --> 01:09:38,203
