1371
01:09:51,509 --> 01:09:53,260
 Follow that orb!

1372
01:10:06,607 --> 01:10:07,983
Incoming!

1373
01:10:11,612 --> 01:10:13,488
What sort of
creature are you?

1374
01:10:13,656 --> 01:10:16,491
The name is Grunion!

1375
01:10:18,953 --> 01:10:20,412
I'm in love!

1376
01:10:23,457 --> 01:10:25,375
I just need to
find a wormhole.

