1388
01:11:07,835 --> 01:11:10,503
Penny, my queen,
I know you're in there.

1389
01:11:11,505 --> 01:11:13,548
We're coming, Shermanus!

1390
01:11:17,595 --> 01:11:18,595
 Time travel failed.

1391
01:11:18,721 --> 01:11:19,679
Mr. Peabody!

1392
01:11:19,764 --> 01:11:20,889
Look out!

1393
01:11:22,975 --> 01:11:24,392
ALL: Whoa!

1394
01:11:30,232 --> 01:11:31,608
Shermanus, hold on.

1395
01:11:31,776 --> 01:11:33,735
We shall release
you from this egg.

1396
01:11:36,906 --> 01:11:39,616
Drop the saber
and step away from
the futuristic orb.

1397
01:11:39,784 --> 01:11:41,951
I take orders from no man!

1398
01:11:48,459 --> 01:11:51,753
Don't tase me, bro.

1399
01:11:52,505 --> 01:11:54,297
Come out, Peabody,
with your paws in the air.

1400
01:11:56,842 --> 01:11:58,677
Mr. Peabody,
you're under arrest...

1401
01:11:58,844 --> 01:12:00,970
