reckless endangerment...

1402
01:12:01,138 --> 01:12:04,432
And a multiplicity
of major traffic violations.

1403
01:12:04,600 --> 01:12:05,475
You don't understand.

1404
01:12:05,643 --> 01:12:07,936
There's a rip
in the space-time continuum!

1405
01:12:08,104 --> 01:12:10,063
If you arrest me,
I won't be able to fix...

1406
01:12:10,231 --> 01:12:12,232
Blah, blah, blah.
For too long...

1407
01:12:12,400 --> 01:12:15,276
you've bamboozled the world
with your fancy jargon...

1408
01:12:15,444 --> 01:12:16,611
and that little
red tie of yours...

1409
01:12:16,779 --> 01:12:18,113
and look what's come of it.

1410
01:12:18,280 --> 01:12:19,197
Take him away!

1411
01:12:19,365 --> 01:12:20,073
Wait.

1412
01:12:21,534 --> 01:12:22,409
Mr. Peabody!

1413
01:12:22,576 --> 01:12:23,576
Sherman!

1414
01:12:25,371 --> 01:12:27,497
What's gonna happen
to Mr. Peabody?

1415
01:12:27,665 --> 01:12:30,625
Don't you know
what happens to
dogs that bite?

1416
01:12:30,793 --> 01:12:32,293
 Let me go.

1417
01:12:32,461 --> 01:12:33,712
You don't know
what you're doing.

1418
01:12:33,879 --> 01:12:35,880
Please, before
it's too late.

1419
01:12:36,006 --> 01:12:37,465
 Wait!

1420
01:12:38,008 --> 01:12:39,467
Give him another chance.

1421
01:12:39,635 --> 01:12:43,388
He's through with chances.
Now, he has to pay
for his mistakes.

1422
01:12:43,681 --> 01:12:45,348
But I'm the one
who made all
the mistakes.

1423
01:12:45,516 --> 01:12:48,268
I'm the one
who used the WABAC
without permission.

1424
01:12:48,436 --> 01:12:51,312
The only mistake
Mr. Peabody ever made...

1425
01:12:52,356 --> 01:12:53,648
was me.

1426
01:12:54,859 --> 01:12:56,234
Sherman.

1427
01:12:56,777 --> 01:12:58,987
You're absolutely
right, Sherman.

1428
01:12:59,155 --> 01:13:03,283
What kind of a father
could this dog
ever be to a boy?

1429
01:13:06,245 --> 01:13:07,871
Maybe you're right,
Ms. Grunion.

1430
01:13:08,038 --> 01:13:10,248
But there's one thing
you haven't considered.

1431
01:13:10,416 --> 01:13:11,499
What's that?

1432
01:13:13,043 --> 01:13:15,044
I'm a dog, too!

1433
01:13:17,047 --> 01:13:19,674
If being a dog
means you're like
Mr. Peabody...

1434
01:13:19,842 --> 01:13:21,634
who never turns
his back on you...

1435
01:13:21,802 --> 01:13:24,679
and who's always there
to pick you up
when you fall...

1436
01:13:24,847 --> 01:13:28,975
and loves you no matter
how many times you mess up...

1437
01:13:29,143 --> 01:13:31,436
if that's what it
means to be a dog...

1438
01:13:31,604 --> 01:13:34,814
then, yeah,
I'm a dog, too!

1439
01:13:36,734 --> 01:13:41,613
I'm a dog, too.

1440
01:13:41,781 --> 01:13:44,574
I'm a dog, too!

1441
01:13:44,742 --> 01:13:45,992
I'm a dog as well!

1442
01:13:46,368 --> 01:13:47,619
A poodle dog!

1443
01:13:47,787 --> 01:13:49,704
I am a dog, too.

1444
01:13:49,872 --> 01:13:51,372
Ditto on that dog thing!

1445
01:13:51,540 --> 01:13:56,044
I'm a dog, too.

