I'm a dog, too.

1450
01:14:18,359 --> 01:14:20,485
I'm Spartacus!

1451
01:14:20,945 --> 01:14:24,864
All right, fine,
you're all dogs, but
you can't change the law.

1452
01:14:25,032 --> 01:14:26,908
I know someone who can.

1453
01:14:28,828 --> 01:14:30,286
George Washington.

1454
01:14:31,872 --> 01:14:35,166
We hold these truths
to be self-evident...

1455
01:14:35,334 --> 01:14:40,964
that all men, and some dogs,
are created equal.

1456
01:14:41,298 --> 01:14:46,052
I hereby award Mr. Peabody
a presidential pardon.

1457
01:14:46,220 --> 01:14:47,303
Me, too.

1458
01:14:47,471 --> 01:14:48,763
I've done worse.

1459
01:14:57,106 --> 01:14:58,773
Huh?

1460
01:15:03,153 --> 01:15:04,487
Uh, Mr. Peabody, look!

1461
01:15:10,119 --> 01:15:11,536
Ahh!

1462
01:15:12,621 --> 01:15:14,205
Ooh!

1463
01:15:17,543 --> 01:15:18,960
It's getting closer!

1464
01:15:19,128 --> 01:15:20,420
What are
we going to do?

1465
01:15:20,796 --> 01:15:22,964
This is the greatest
collection of geniuses
ever assembled!

1466
01:15:23,132 --> 01:15:26,009
Surely we can come
up with another way
of getting to the past.

1467
01:15:26,468 --> 01:15:27,802
I can build a catapult.

1468
01:15:27,970 --> 01:15:29,429
We go very fast.

1469
