gravitational field...

1486
01:16:23,609 --> 01:16:25,401
that's equal and opposite...

1487
01:16:25,569 --> 01:16:28,863
to the rip in
the space-time continuum!

1488
01:16:30,115 --> 01:16:31,783
 Oh, my...

1489
01:16:31,951 --> 01:16:33,326
