1490
01:16:33,494 --> 01:16:37,080
We're gonna fly up there
and punch that big
hole in the face!

1491
01:16:37,498 --> 01:16:38,289
Yes!

1492
01:16:40,000 --> 01:16:43,169
Sherman, you're a genius.

1493
01:16:44,713 --> 01:16:45,797
But, Peabody...

1494
01:16:45,881 --> 01:16:48,591
how far into
the future must you go?

1495
01:16:48,759 --> 01:16:50,551
Just a few seconds
ought to do it,

1496
01:16:50,678 --> 01:16:52,428
and then we'll
slingshot right back.

1497
01:16:52,596 --> 01:16:54,472
Are you sure this
is going to work?

1498
01:16:54,640 --> 01:16:56,099
Don't worry, Penny.

1499
01:16:56,642 --> 01:16:58,351
Just remember,
I'm a... 

