1512
01:18:05,961 --> 01:18:07,712
Sherman, we need more speed.

1513
01:18:11,008 --> 01:18:12,175
Now?

1514
01:18:12,342 --> 01:18:13,968
Just a little more!

1515
01:18:14,219 --> 01:18:15,636
(SHUDDERS)

1516
