Farewell!

1521
01:19:08,273 --> 01:19:09,440
Ooh!

1522
01:19:09,525 --> 01:19:11,776
You haven't seen
the last of me,
Peabody.

1523
01:19:11,944 --> 01:19:15,154
You'll make
a mistake eventually,
and when you do...

1524
01:19:15,322 --> 01:19:17,490
I'll be there!

1525
01:19:17,658 --> 01:19:19,283
The Grunion is mine!
Ooh!

1526
01:19:40,013 --> 01:19:43,141
Come on, Sherman. Come on!

